{"tid":908674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"調查發現　越不普教中　成積越好","createTime":"2018-11-19T17:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T08:08:37.000Z","uid":47714,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"294ffe5643b32ab2e9cb737e96467bb5c1cf46b3","tid":908674,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T17:49:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/photos/a.636947586361970/2041545195902195/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkonglangstudies%2Fphotos%2Fa.636947586361970%2F2041545195902195%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=Kw%2FU6yUwWLd772NRwAvJUQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=faecafda\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/photos/a.636947586361970/2041545195902195/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：港語學<br />\n<br />\n全港中小學中文科教學語言資料庫 2017/18 年度普查，本會試將不同「收生組別」內「以普通話教授中國語文科」中學比例製成橫向棒形圖，赫見 Band 1A 中學搞「普教中」比例最低（ 11.63% ）、 Band 1B 次低（ 20.93% ）、 Band 1C （ 29.41% ）高於 Band 1B 而低於其餘組別（ 30.77% ）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/roXTL5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FroXTL5&h=bc6aa867&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"628f3914527cf54dce41c9ec7a1c79c733aa7624","tid":908674,"uid":55597,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T18:07:11.000Z","msg":"正常<br />\n蟲語同蟲文根本就唔文學根基，用得多只會搞到 D 人唔識字、唔識講、唔識聽、唔識讀"},{"pid":"9fdd43992525104fcb1ab87e16258b4046398610","tid":908674,"uid":102973,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T18:09:18.000Z","msg":"睇黎樓豬深受普教中影響 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e9aeae34cb8c1fcb3b41298e5e421ed97f855b","tid":908674,"uid":137743,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T18:47:20.000Z","msg":"普教中根本on9"},{"pid":"66033957c463937e67